---
description: Go config struct and YAML file annotation rules
globs: "**/*.go,**/config*.yaml,**/config*.yml"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Config Annotation Rules (MUST follow)

配置结构体和配置文件**必须**保持注释同步。

## Rule 1: 枚举/多选值必须列出所有可选项

字段有多个可选值时，**MUST** 在行尾注释中用 `|` 分隔列出全部选项。

```go
// Good
Driver string `mapstructure:"driver"` // "sqlite3" | "postgres"
Level  string `mapstructure:"level"`  // "debug" | "info" | "warn" | "error" | "fatal"
Mode   string `mapstructure:"mode"`   // "openldap" | "activedirectory"

// Bad — 缺少可选值
Driver string `mapstructure:"driver"`
Level  string `mapstructure:"level"` // log level
```

## Rule 2: 复杂参数必须加详细说明

含单位、默认值、特殊格式的字段，**MUST** 在注释中说明。

```go
// Good
MaxSize    int    `mapstructure:"max_size"`     // max size per file in MB
MaxAge     int    `mapstructure:"max_age"`      // max days to retain old files
Path       string `mapstructure:"path"`         // SQLite file path, e.g. "data/app.db"
SSLMode    string `mapstructure:"sslmode"`      // "disable" | "require" | "verify-ca" | "verify-full"

// Bad — 无单位、无示例
MaxSize int    `mapstructure:"max_size"`
Path    string `mapstructure:"path"`
```

## Rule 3: YAML 配置文件必须加对应注释

Go 结构体中的可选值和说明，**MUST** 同步写到 YAML 配置文件中。

```yaml
# Good — 段落上方列出可选值，行内注释说明
# driver: sqlite3 | postgres
database:
  driver: sqlite3
  path: data/app.db

# level: debug | info | warn | error | fatal
# format: text | json
log:
  level: "info"
  format: "text"
  rotate:
    max_size: 100          # 单文件最大 MB
    max_age: 7             # 保留天数

# Bad — 无注释
database:
  driver: sqlite3
log:
  level: "info"
  rotate:
    max_size: 100
```
